│     The logic at line 1260 incorrectly assumes that if `E`   │
│ is not a constant, it must have been part of the cloned loop │
│ body and therefore present in `VMap`. Since `%mul` is not in │
│ `VMap`, `VMap.lookup(E)` returns a default-constructed       │
│ `WeakTrackingVH` which points to `nullptr`. Dereferencing    │
│ this triggers the assertion.                                 │
